# Data Directory

This directory should contain the dataset for the project.

## Required File

- `arabic_sentiment_reviews.csv` - The main dataset file

## Download Instructions

### Option 1: Kaggle API

```bash
kaggle datasets download -d abdallaellaithy/330k-arabic-sentiment-reviews
unzip 330k-arabic-sentiment-reviews.zip -d data/
```

### Option 2: Manual Download

1. Visit: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/abdallaellaithy/330k-arabic-sentiment-reviews
2. Download the dataset
3. Extract `arabic_sentiment_reviews.csv` to this folder

## Dataset Information

- **Size**: ~330,000 reviews
- **Format**: CSV
- **Columns**:
  - `content`: Arabic review text
  - `label`: Sentiment label (positive/negative)

## Note

This folder is excluded from version control (`.gitignore`) due to the large file size.
